text: Robin Bakker (born 4 December 1959) is an Australian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
